#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.degrees.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.degrees"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.degrees.degrees:1 of
msgid "Convert angles from radians to degrees."
msgstr "将角度从弧度转换为度。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.degrees.degrees of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.degrees.degrees:3 of
msgid "Input tensor in radians."
msgstr "以弧度为单位的输入张量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.degrees.degrees:5 of
msgid ""
"A location into which the result is stored. If provided, it must have a "
"shape that the inputs broadcast to. If not provided or `None`, a freshly-"
"allocated tensor is returned. A tuple (possible only as a keyword "
"argument) must have length equal to the number of outputs."
msgstr ""
"用于存储结果的位置。如果提供，其形状必须与输入广播一致。如果未提供或为 `"
"None`，则返回一个新分配的张量。元组（只能作为关键字参数）的长度必须等于"
"输出的数量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.degrees.degrees:10 of
msgid ""
"Values of True indicate to calculate the ufunc at that position, values "
"of False indicate to leave the value in the output alone."
msgstr "值为 True 表示在该位置计算 ufunc，值为 False 表示保留输出中的值不变。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.degrees.degrees of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.degrees.degrees:15 of
msgid ""
"**y** -- The corresponding degree values; if `out` was supplied this is a"
" reference to it."
msgstr "**y** -- 对应的度数值；如果提供了 `out`，则这是对它的引用。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.degrees.degrees of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.degrees.degrees:21 of
msgid ":py:obj:`rad2deg`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.degrees.degrees:22 of
msgid "equivalent function"
msgstr "等效函数"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.degrees.degrees:25 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.degrees.degrees:26 of
msgid "Convert a radian array to degrees"
msgstr "将弧度数组转换为度"

